OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FWater companies sorry over 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fspilling raw sewage        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, England's water and sewage companies   
OL,6, have apologised for not "acting quickly
OL,7, enough" to tackle sewage spills.       
OL,9,FThey have faced mounting public anger  
OL,10,Fover continued spilling of raw sewage  
OL,11,Finto rivers and seas.                  
OL,13,FIn 2022, raw sewage was dumped into    
OL,14,Frivers and seas for 1.75 million hours 
OL,15,F- or 825 times a day on average.       
OL,17,FCampaigners welcomed the apology but   
OL,18,Fsaid they would wait to see whether the
OL,19,Fpromises delivered change.             
